snippet.title: Cosmic Star Heroine - Gameplay Preview | PS Underground, PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/cosmic-star-heroine-ps4/

Cosmic Star Heroine launches this week on PS4 as part of the Play Collective weekly releases! Check out 12 minutes of hands-on gameplay in this episode of PS Underground hosted by Ryan Clements and Justin Massongill, and embrace the sweet style and hilarious tone of this love letter to JPRGs.
